{"tid":1759221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區選有用 文宣有用 和理非有用 前線都有用","createTime":"2019-11-27T13:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T05:39:15.000Z","uid":44559,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0e67936e2564ef6fd0e8ff0572a50a052ffed50d","tid":1759221,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"有好多人出黎開post 話區選無用，又話咩體制爛，得個講字，點都要出黎前線打<br />\n<br />\n你地明唔明而家係全面抗爭；攬炒巴海外戰線、海外登報、文宣，和理非，遊行、前線佔領全部都好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n區選多一個位就多一分資源，請多個手足，區議會又多個位發聲，拉攏淺藍，外國又睇區選做民意，唔好再話咩無用呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抗爭既重點係兄弟爬山，各自扶持；唔止講人；每樣有用既方法都要做！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家可能好多手足迷惑，唔知做咩好/覺得件事完左，其實未架！ <br />\n<br />\n文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放映會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得理工有手足比人踩頭，有過千手足比狗拉<br />\n<br />\n而家連文宣都會比狗咬呀！ 繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4341967058f54bcd7ecff0f9f7350e3d98ef26","tid":1759221,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f306ec03158c18222ea891ae43a4ca945ab0e3","tid":1759221,"uid":139315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:45:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"57f3113a0bd84576f3349ff18fea1145d290ab80","tid":1759221,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e67936e2564ef6fd0e8ff0572a50a052ffed50d","tid":1759221,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"有好多人出黎開post 話區選無用，又話咩體制爛，得個講字，點都要出黎前線打<br />\n<br />\n你地明唔明而家係全面抗爭；攬炒巴海外戰線、海外登報、文宣，和理非，遊行、前線佔領全部都好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n區選多一個位就多一分資源，請多個手足，區議會又多個位發聲，拉攏淺藍，外國又睇區選做民意，唔好再話咩無用呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抗爭既重點係兄弟爬山，各自扶持；唔止講人；每樣有用既方法都要做！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家可能好多手足迷惑，唔知做咩好/覺得件事完左，其實未架！ <br />\n<br />\n文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放映會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得理工有手足比人踩頭，有過千手足比狗拉<br />\n<br />\n而家連文宣都會比狗咬呀！ 繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d55dba9f99237cc027dea0f502028c4064782df","tid":1759221,"uid":331459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">贏左場架，輸左個家！</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1759145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1759145</a>"},{"pid":"8ea695859fbad6786f73fb5b80f3a25d5ecf20d5","tid":1759221,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:46:28.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：我地今鋪無輸的念頭<br />\n<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家80%, 仲差少少</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=dc0ae372\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=921e36e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n.<br />\n(對唔住，雖然區選迎來短暫的勝利，但要做ge 野都要持績落去，唔好放軟手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手足，星期四愛丁堡見)"},{"pid":"ff44e4a0297f135eea48e6fcd5da365411e75852","tid":1759221,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6f74498b7e75